name: Under The Sea for Person with Thalassophobia
description:
A receipt Under The Sea for Person with Thalassophobia.

A person with thalassophobia may be afraid of the vastness or emptiness of the ocean, the sea creatures in the water, or both. Thalassophobia is different from aquaphobia, which is a fear of water itself.

Thalassophobia could also be caused by traumatic events. A childhood near-drowning experience, witnessing a shark attack, never learning to swim, or even being told scary stories of the ocean are just a few examples of possible events that could trigger thalassophobia.

I hope this NFT can make the person with Thalassophobia want to go swim Under The Sea with me.
